(16979925, '', 'Applicant 297', 14465892, 'Grooves ''Get your groove on''', 28, 2.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 5, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'Yorkshire and The Humber', 'Normanton, Pontefract and Castleford', 'West Yorkshire', 'Wakefield', 0, 'Y', 0, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Dance', '#REF!', 'Yorkshire', 'We are targeting young people from areas of high deprivation, children with disabilities, minority ethnic communities and other ''hard to reach'' groups such as the settled gypsy and traveller community. The funding will be used to provide a Dance showcase event which all of the listed groups can participate in.'),
