(16982865, '', 'Applicant 300', 1466562, '''By Any Means'' Sheffield Open Weekend activity', 28, 10.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 10, 10, 5, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Organisation', 'Yorkshire and The Humber', 'Sheffield Central', 'South Yorkshire', 'Sheffield', 6, 'Y', 1, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Combined arts', '#REF!', 'Yorkshire', 'Sheffield will celebrate Open Weekend, one year to the opening of the Olympic Games 2012. A variety of events will take place across Sheffield over the weekend of 22 - 24 July. The central event will be an Olympic-inspired creative event on Tudor Square entitled 2012 By Any Means.'),
