(16983645, '', 'Applicant 307', 14275324, 'Othello by Verdi  - November 2011', 26, 5.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 13, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'South East', 'Mole Valley', 'Surrey', 'Guildford', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 7, 0, 0, 'Ot', 'Music', '#REF!', 'South East', 'A fully staged production sung in English with an 11 piece orchestra using a specially commissioned orchestral reduction. \n\n4 public performances\n\nGrant funding is sought specifically to support orchestral fees of '),
