(16987155, '', 'Applicant 310', 16987153, '''circuit'' - East Midlands performance platform', 1, 4.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 4, 4, 6, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Individual', 'East Midlands', 'Leicester South', 'Leicester', 'Leicester', 3, 'N', 1, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Theatre', '#REF!', 'East Midlands', '''circuit'' is a platform for new, emerging and current contemporary performance/Live Art practitioners, from the East Midlands, (Leicester, Sheffield, Loughborough, Nottingham and Derby), to show work at De Montfort University'),
(16988466, '', 'Applicant 311', 13137014, 'BINGO', 1, 10.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 5, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'London', 'Camberwell and Peckham', 'Greater London', 'Southwark', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Music', '#REF!', 'London', 'Ensemble Amorpha will commission 7 composers to write new works for a contemporary music, popular sub-culture and theatrical event. BINGO, inspired by and incorporating the rules and rituals of a bingo evening, complete with comp'),
(16989460, '', 'Applicant 312', 16989453, 'Battle Arts Trail - The World Turned Upside Down', 1, 9.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 9, 9, 6, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Organisation', 'South East', 'Bexhill and Battle', 'East Sussex', 'Rother', 18, 'Y', 1, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Visual arts', '#REF!', 'South East', 'An Art Trail comprising works created by commissioned local artists as well as resulting from professionally led commmunity workshops.  The theme of the trail is ''The World Turned Upside Down'' and it is intended to provide something extraordinary which jolts us out of our daily familiarity with our environment.'),
