(17084919, '', 'Applicant 454', 17084912, 'Theatrical experience through time', 10, 6.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 19, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'North East', 'Newcastle upon Tyne Central', 'Tyne and Wear', 'Newcastle upon Tyne', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 6, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Theatre', '#REF!', 'North East', 'We are creating a multi dimensional performance project that uses the environment of the Tyne Theatre to create engaging characters, theatrical images and social history for young people and new audiences.  The project builds on the artistic and theatrical experience of professionals, passing on skills and developing new talent.\n\nA'),
