(17163404, '', 'Applicant 551', 17163402, 'Cissie', 20, 10.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 19, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Individual', 'London', 'Hackney South and Shoreditch', 'Greater London', 'Hackney', 0, 'Y', 0, '6 weeks', 4, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Theatre', '#REF!', 'London', '"The Cissie Project" is a re-imagining/re-working of  play I wrote and staged in 2008, South Africa. It looks at the life and times of the anti-apartheid activist Cissie Gool and explores and narrates the memory of the neighbourhood, District Six, before and after Forced Removals.'),
