(17217712, '', 'Applicant 629', 1624292, 'Women at the HeART', 24, 30.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 23, 23, 15, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Organisation', 'South East', 'Buckingham', 'Buckinghamshire', 'Aylesbury Vale', 6, 'N', 1, '12 weeks', 12, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Visual arts', '#REF!', 'South East', 'Women at the HeART seeks sustained ways of using the the expertise and creative practice of visual artists and the arts to empower vulnerable and disadvantaged women, and the networks that support them, whilst also encouraging team teaching and shared professional development between experienced and newly emerging artists.'),
