(17225984, '', 'Applicant 641', 1638656, 'FORMotion Pilot Archiving Project - Phase 2 R & D', 25, 26.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 26, 26, 28, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Organisation', 'Yorkshire and The Humber', 'Dewsbury', 'West Yorkshire', 'Kirklees', 5, 'N', 1, '12 weeks', 14, 0, 0, 'Ot', 'Dance', '#REF!', 'Yorkshire', 'We have been funded by Yorkshire Forward to research and develop our new archiving software titled FORMotion. This Pilot Project will research further, test and evaluate use of the software to archive old and new dance works for Northern Ballet and for Phoenix Dance Theatre.'),
