(17262518, '', 'Applicant 704', 1629723, 'Hansel & Gretel Education Programme', 29, 4.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 4, 0, 4, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'South West', 'Chippenham', 'Wiltshire', 'Wiltshire', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Music', '#REF!', 'South West', 'Professionally led music workshops in 2 schools of challenging demographic (in urban areas of deprivation with high proportion of special educational needs and behavioural difficulties), followed by specially adapted children''s performance of Humperdinck''s opera, Hansel & Gretel by professional cast and orchestra.  CPD for local teachers between workshop sessions.'),
