(17482488, '', 'Applicant 1203', 17482480, 'Express Yourself Workshops', 3, 9.0, 'Yes', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 5, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'Eastern', 'Great Yarmouth', 'Norfolk', 'Great Yarmouth', 0, 'Y', 0, '6 weeks', 0, 1, 1, 'Ot', 'Combined arts', '#REF!', 'East', 'We would like to expand our services offering more to our existing pupils as well as young people in the surrounding area. Express Yourself workshops will aim to give inspiration to both pupils and staff. The workshops are to be based around Media, Musical Theatre, Dance, Acting and Arts & Crafts.'),
