(17495786, '', 'Applicant 1225', 1841990, 'SoundSpiral', 4, 74.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 81, 81, 27, 'Q2', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Individual', 'East Midlands', 'Lincoln', 'Lincolnshire', 'Lincoln', 12, 'Y', 1, '12 weeks', 12, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Combined arts', '#REF!', 'East Midlands', 'Large scale Sound Installation including mother-tongue speakers of 40 different languages, and their respective communities. The work will explore themes of ''uncovering unity in diversity''. It will also leave a massive legacy of hardware, software and resource for other practitioners and participants to benefit from and build on.'),
