(17593098, '', 'Applicant 1446', 17593096, '''Portraits in the Making'' Pitzhanger Exhibition', 18, 9.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 9, 9, 21, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Individual', 'Eastern', 'North East Hertfordshire', 'Hertfordshire', 'North Hertfordshire', 1, 'N', 1, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Visual arts', '#REF!', 'East', '''Portraits in the Making'' is a multidisciplinary exhibition by a group of emerging designer makers selected for the Crafts Councils Hothouse Programme.  The artists will be responding to the historic Pitzhanger Manor House and engaging the community with the venue and a variety of contemporary craft, art and design processes.'),
