(17597382, '', 'Applicant 1450', 1639376, 'Engagement with wider performance opportunities', 18, 9.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 21, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'Yorkshire and The Humber', 'Barnsley Central', 'South Yorkshire', 'Barnsley', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Dance', '#REF!', 'Yorkshire', 'This activity is to enable Qdos Creates to develop and raise the profile of its existing ''Young People''s Program'' by delivering six different mini-projects that have a performance opportunities aligned to them, some of which are linked to Barnsley Council town centre events.\n\n'),
(17597535, '', 'Applicant 1451', 17597526, 'Word Sound Have Power', 18, 2.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 21, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'London', 'Tooting', 'Greater London', 'Wandsworth', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Theatre', '#REF!', 'London', 'A series of performance nights and workshops focusing on social cohesion of socially excluded groups. Performers to come from areas of criminal justice, refugee status, homelessness, drug addiction etc ... Focus to be on creating dialogue about the use of arts for social cohesion, both in the UK and internationally.'),
