(17599603, '', 'Applicant 1455', 4471860, '5th Manchester Kurdish Film Festival', 18, 3.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 21, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'North West', 'Manchester Central', 'Greater Manchester', 'Manchester', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Combined arts', '#REF!', 'North West', 'We are seeking funding for the opening event which will consist of an art exhibition featuring 18 international artists. Following the art exhibition there will be a live concert featuring two popular Kurdish singers, accompanied by a live orchestra at the Zion Arts Centre in Manchester.'),
