(17600908, '', 'Applicant 1457', 17600906, 'Black Bull Folk and Blues Festival', 18, 3.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 21, 'Q1', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Individual', 'North West', 'Penrith and The Border', 'Cumbria', 'Eden', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Music', '#REF!', 'North West', 'The Black Bull Music Festival is run for the enjoyment of the local community and brings together musicians from England, Ireland and Scotland. The music festival consists of afternoon jamming sessions and evening performances. Next year, we would like to incorporate a number of teaching workshops.'),
