(17698218, '', 'Applicant 1692', 1617682, '''Stranger in a Raincoat'' Research and Development.', 1, 2.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 2, 2, 5, 'Q2', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Organisation', 'North West', 'Liverpool, Riverside', 'Merseyside', 'Liverpool', 28, 'N', 1, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Theatre', '#REF!', 'North West', 'Our activity will be a two week period of concentrated devising that will form the basis of a new show.  We will explore ideas related to chance and randomness, whilst using strong storytelling and creating potent theatrical imagery .  We aim to present fifty minutes of material at a ''scratch'' performance.'),
