(17779113, '', 'Applicant 1846', 1626221, 'Oedipussy', 9, 77.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 77, 77, 1, 'Q2', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', 'National activities', 1, 'Organisation', 'South East', 'Brighton, Pavilion', 'Brighton and Hove', 'Brighton and Hove', 27, 'N', 1, '12 weeks', 12, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Theatre', '#REF!', 'South East', 'We are looking to produce and deliver a eleven week mid-scale tour of a new comedy theatre work, Oedipussy, directed by Emma Rice and co-produced by The Royal & Derngate Northampton'),
