(17882484, '', 'Applicant 2024', 17882482, 'Soca Saga Boys: A Carnival Float and Sound', 21, 9.0, 'Yes', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 5, 'Q2', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Individual', 'London', 'West Ham', 'Greater London', 'Newham', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 2, 1, 1, 'Ot', 'Combined arts', '#REF!', 'London', 'Our main activity is to perform as a Sound/Fete, accompanied by a Mas Band section of Performers. We are based around the specific culture of Carnival. We will be working with young adults and teenagers of the community, although we appeal to an audience of all ages.'),
