(18106581, '', 'Applicant 2432', 18106579, 'The Gambler', 17, 7.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 7, 7, 23, 'Q2', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Individual', 'London', 'Tottenham', 'Greater London', 'Haringey', 7, 'N', 1, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Theatre', '#REF!', 'London', 'We want to develop daring, evocative and engaging physical theatre, through a complete collaborative process, around the theme of addiction. We also aim at engaging public audiences to take part in the research, to ensure that the work remains fresh, vital and relevant to today'),
