(18175338, '', 'Applicant 2599', 18175330, 'Diverse Music for Individuals and Communities.', 25, 8.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 31, 'Q2', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'Yorkshire and The Humber', 'Bradford East', 'West Yorkshire', 'Bradford', 0, 'Y', 0, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Music', '#REF!', 'Yorkshire', 'We want to train two groups of adult people in our community and create a package of diverse music that reflects different cultures and races that make up our community. They will be performing the music as their occupation and as a means of meeting our community''s artistic needs.'),
