(18176324, '', 'Applicant 2602', 1387365, 'Pushing the boundaries', 25, 80.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 130, 80, 5, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 2, 'Organisation', 'North West', 'Oldham East and Saddleworth', 'Greater Manchester', 'Oldham', 1, 'Y', 1, '12 weeks', 10, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Theatre', '#REF!', 'North West', 'Oldham Coliseum Theatre Company will vacate the theatre in early 2012 whilst it undergoes refurbishment. Whilst in exile, the company will work in several new settings to develop a variety of novel projects that will attract new audiences, promote artistic innovation and learning, furthering significant organisational development.'),
