(18213981, '', 'Applicant 2678', 1624472, '''Accidental Death'' Development and Adaptation', 29, 13.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 13, 0, 2, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'South East', 'Winchester', 'Hampshire', 'Winchester', 0, 'N', 0, '12 weeks', 14, 0, 0, 'Ot', 'Theatre', '#REF!', 'South East', 'We are seeking funding for a multimedia production based on the play ''Accidental Death of An Anarchist'' by Dario Fo for performance by prisoners in West Hill HMP Winchester.  The intention is to adapt and update the play in order to create a contemporary context relevant to the prisoners.'),
