(18214853, '', 'Applicant 2684', 1816401, 'Psychotherapy', 29, 7.0, 'Yes', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 10, 'Q2', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Individual', 'South East', 'Gillingham and Rainham', 'Medway', 'Medway', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 2, 1, 1, 'Ot', 'Literature', '#REF!', 'South East', 'To complete a book, primarily autobiographical, based on the mismaking of my only feature film, Psychotherapy, which I wrote and directed in 1992.  In which I''ll be trying to understand my own sense of failure through the (perceived) failures of others, mostly specific to the British film industry.\n'),
