(18215765, '', 'Applicant 2686', 1463602, 'Shadowball Tour', 29, 49.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 49, 49, 26, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', 'National activities', 1, 'Organisation', 'London', 'Hackney South and Shoreditch', 'Greater London', 'Hackney', 25, 'Y', 1, '12 weeks', 13, 0, 0, 'Ot', 'Music', '#REF!', 'London', 'Shadowball links a jazz opera project by Julian Joseph about black baseball players and their jazz compatriots to a sports programme for primary schools and communities. Following the premiere and school residencies, it will tour London and beyond, inspiring young people to have the determination to achieve their dreams.'),
