(18216414, '', 'Applicant 2689', 18216412, 'Art class', 29, 5.0, 'Yes', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 4, 'Q2', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Individual', 'London', 'Lewisham East', 'Greater London', 'Lewisham', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 1, 1, 1, 'Ot', 'Visual arts', '#REF!', 'London', 'I work in a hostel for women with mental health and drug issues as a support worker, I have studied art at college and Goldsmiths university. I am very passionate about starting an art class here for the residents, I feel it would be very theraputical and beneficial to them.'),
