(18490839, '', 'Applicant 3243', 18490832, 'The Firewatchers', 31, 6.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 6, 0, 4, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'London', 'Hackney North and Stoke Newington', 'Greater London', 'Hackney', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Theatre', '#REF!', 'London', 'Our activity deals with wartime, feminism and the daily heroism in london during World War Two. More specifically: two women working together as firewatchers and how the war could bring those with different social backgrounds together in a common effort to fight it.\n'),
