(18491024, '', 'Applicant 3245', 18491017, 'Jubilee 2012', 1, 10.0, 'Yes', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 14, 'Q2', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'Eastern', 'Bury St Edmunds', 'Suffolk', 'Mid Suffolk', 0, 'Y', 0, '6 weeks', 2, 1, 1, 'Ot', 'Combined arts', '#REF!', 'East', 'Held on 4th June 2012,  celebrating the Queen''s Diamond Jubilee;  we aim to hold a free Arts centred event for the whole  community, especially those who do not normally engage with the Arts. Activities include musicians, artistes & dramatists, local voluntary and community arts groups, community  impromptu singing,  drama,  magic.'),
