(18494053, '', 'Applicant 3250', 18494046, 'Creative Branches Website', 2, 10.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 11, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'West Midlands', 'Wyre Forest', 'Worcestershire', 'Wyre Forest', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 6, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Visual arts', '#REF!', 'West Midlands', 'Creative Branches is a website designed to help the next generation of creative talent become successful by bridging the gap from education to the creative industry. It will be a dynamic creative social community where students can showcase their artistic work to the world.'),
