(18529234, '', 'Applicant 3328', 18529232, 'Fashion Collection', 8, 3.0, 'Yes', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 13, 'Q2', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Individual', 'South East', 'Brighton, Pavilion', 'Brighton and Hove', 'Brighton and Hove', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 1, 1, 1, 'Ot', 'Visual arts', '#REF!', 'South East', 'I''m a freelance Fashion Designer. I want to create a collection, then display it in my website, in other directories, and online shops .The fund will be used in order to follow the whole process from design, going through the elaboration, until reaching the publicity point.  \n\n\n\n'),
