(18529862, '', 'Applicant 3330', 18529860, 'GLI.TC/H', 9, 2.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 2, 2, 18, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Individual', 'West Midlands', 'Birmingham, Ladywood', 'West Midlands', 'Birmingham', 25, 'N', 1, '6 weeks', 6, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Visual arts', '#REF!', 'West Midlands', 'GLI.TC/H is a physical and virtual assembly of artists, hackers, circuit benders and those who find wonder in that which others call broken. Now in its second year GLI.TC/H will take place in Chicago, Illinois, Amsterdam, Netherlands and Birmingham, UK'),
