(18566920, '', 'Applicant 3408', 18566918, 'study at Italia Conti and Move to London', 14, 5.0, 'Yes', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 28, 'Q2', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Individual', 'Yorkshire and The Humber', 'Doncaster Central', 'South Yorkshire', 'Doncaster', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 2, 1, 1, 'Ot', 'Theatre', '#REF!', 'Yorkshire', 'Due to Nancy''s vast experience in acting, we need to find a better drama school, we need money to attend Italia Conti and we also need to move to London, as advised by our agent, to gain more work, we are losing work, due to our location'),
