(18569640, '', 'Applicant 3411', 18569636, 'PERESTROIKA: RECONSTRUCTED', 14, 9.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 9, 9, 19, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Individual', 'South East', 'Canterbury', 'Kent', 'Canterbury', 1, 'N', 1, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Visual arts', '#REF!', 'South East', 'Perestroika: Reconstructed will re-mix, develop and extend my acclaimed film, Perestroika, into two sequences. '),
