(18581278, '', 'Applicant 3435', 1821390, 'International Women''s Day Project (title tbc)', 16, 17.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 17, 17, 30, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Individual', 'South West', 'Totnes', 'Devon', 'South Hams', 2, 'Y', 1, '12 weeks', 11, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Dance', '#REF!', 'South West', 'This application is an artist-led commission of a programme of new cross-art performance work from four Devon-based female choreographers. The collaborative work will be performed at 5 venues in the Southwest inspired by International Women''s Day. The project will create new opportunities for artists and audiences.'),
