(18612159, '', 'Applicant 3514', 9052204, 'Theatre Gloucestershire', 21, 30.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 30, 30, 14, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Organisation', 'South West', 'Gloucester', 'Gloucestershire', 'Gloucester', 6, 'Y', 1, '12 weeks', 12, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Theatre', '#REF!', 'South West', 'Theatre Gloucestershire wants to increase and strengthen theatre practice in the county, focusing on quality, access and audience development. Our main aims are to be the strategic voice for theatre development in the county, raise standards, support new work and emerging artists, develop youth theatre and promote collaboration.'),
(18612341, '', 'Applicant 3515', 18612339, 'Body adornment captured.', 21, 6.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 26, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Individual', 'North East', 'Jarrow', 'Tyne and Wear', 'Gateshead', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Visual arts', '#REF!', 'North East', 'This is a photographic project incorporating studio and location photography to explore body adornment and extension, by recording and building narratives around the work of Jenny Allinson''s sculptural pieces. It will employ tradition and digital techniques to create atmospheric and resonant images that capture this new collaboration.'),
