(18658017, '', 'Applicant 3626', 1599829, 'Jewish Book Week', 27, 28.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 28, 28, 13, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Organisation', 'London', 'Holborn and St Pancras', 'Greater London', 'Camden', 5, 'Y', 1, '12 weeks', 11, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Literature', '#REF!', 'London', 'In 2012, Jewish Book Week is celebrating its 60th anniversary and will for the first time ever be part of the programme of a state of the art mainstream venue. On this occasion, the festival wants to get the visibility it deserves and make a successful transition to Kings Place.'),
(18658131, '', 'Applicant 3627', 18658120, 'ensemblebash @ 20', 27, 46.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 46, 0, 14, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', 'National activities', 0, 'Organisation', 'London', 'West Ham', 'Greater London', 'Newham', 0, 'N', 0, '12 weeks', 11, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Music', '#REF!', 'London', 'The activity will comprise a series of workshops and concerts around the country in a wide variety of venues to celebrate the 20th anniversary of ensemblebash. The concerts will include at least three new commissions from leading British composers and will explore all avenues of the quartet''s activities.'),
(18659722, '', 'Applicant 3628', 1635136, 'Without Planning Permission', 28, 44.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 44, 44, 14, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Organisation', 'West Midlands', 'Tamworth', 'Staffordshire', 'Tamworth', 5, 'Y', 1, '12 weeks', 11, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Theatre', '#REF!', 'West Midlands', 'This is an interactive performance project that is planned to tour to two regions; West and East Midlands.  Each performance involves both interactive and performance elements on themes of citizenship,  community and kinship.  Venues will primarily be community venues.'),
