(18676122, '', 'Applicant 3648', 18676120, 'Mass Genesis of Freedom', 29, 33.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 33, 0, 13, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Individual', 'London', 'Leyton and Wanstead', 'Greater London', 'Waltham Forest', 0, 'Y', 0, '12 weeks', 11, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Visual arts', '#REF!', 'London', 'Centred around the disciplines of art that help to produce the annual Notting Hill Carnival, Kevin intends to produce an exhibition of 50 large photographic images with accompanying video interviews, highlighting the intimate presence of individuals and their contributions over the last 50 years.\n\n'),
