(18978139, '', 'Applicant 4163', 1630494, 'Hot Air', 1, 8.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 8, 8, 13, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Organisation', 'South West', 'Bristol South', 'Bristol, City of', 'Bristol, City of', 3, 'Y', 1, '6 weeks', 6, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Theatre', '#REF!', 'South West', 'We want to research and develop a new piece of professional theatre and participation project that celebrates and investigates hot air ballooning as part of Bristol''s cultural and industrial life, whilst exploring the impact of the current social and economic climate on the lives of vulnerable people in Bristol.'),
