(18983107, '', 'Applicant 4177', 12471126, 'A thing like you and me: a screening programme', 2, 3.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 3, 3, 6, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Individual', 'Yorkshire and The Humber', 'Leeds West', 'West Yorkshire', 'Leeds', 21, 'N', 1, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Visual arts', '#REF!', 'Yorkshire', 'The production of a year-long programme of artist work in the moving image that will explore the video essay as an aesthetic medium that is often overlooked. This will consist of six screening events with artists Ursula Biemann, Yael Bartana, Marie Voignier, Mathieu  Abonnenc, Angela Melitopoulos and Maria Ruido'),
(18985252, '', 'Applicant 4178', 18985244, 'The Van Man', 2, 9.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 9, 9, 7, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Organisation', 'London', 'Hackney South and Shoreditch', 'Greater London', 'Hackney', 22, 'Y', 1, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Dance', '#REF!', 'London', 'We are creating a new contemporary dance theatre work for outdoor touring entitled The Van Man with a supporting educational workshop. We are looking to build on our current repertoire and produce a new work that is exciting, engaging and accessible to new audiences.'),
(18985497, '', 'Applicant 4179', 18985486, 'Creative Writing for special communities.', 2, 8.0, 'Yes', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 14, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Individual', 'South West', 'Chippenham', 'Wiltshire', 'Wiltshire', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 2, 1, 1, 'Ot', 'Literature', '#REF!', 'South West', 'The planned activity is to engage people in the creative arts of poetry and short stories in order to express themselves.. I will tour hospitals, special schools, institutions for the elderly and young offenders institutions throughout the south west. The touring party will consist of myself and student writers.'),
