(19372489, '', 'Applicant 4894', 19372481, '2012 Olympic, Paralympic Games & Cultural Olympiad', 9, 80.0, 'Yes', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 16, 'Q3', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Organisation', 'London', 'Ilford South', 'Greater London', 'Redbridge', 0, 'Y', 0, '12 weeks', 1, 1, 1, 'Ot', 'Not art form specific', '#REF!', 'London', 'Funding deploy our: \n\n*  2012 Olympic, Paralympic Games & Cultural Olympiad Project inclusively with Partners i.e Golden Tours. As National Activities, our Project would significantly develop UK Tourism/Arts inclusively in underdeveloped areas & also engage/stimulate/influence audiences both within / outside our region.\n\n*  Leisure/IT/Telco/Financial Services'),
