(19384369, '', 'Applicant 4919', 17349408, 'A Place Glowing a Brilliant Red', 13, 10.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 0, 0, 17, 'Q4', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Individual', 'London', 'West Ham', 'Greater London', 'Newham', 0, 'Y', 0, '6 weeks', 5, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Combined arts', '#REF!', 'London', 'A Place Glowing a Brilliant Red is a multi-arts collaboration (choreography, musical orchestra) about the near future of humanity on planet Mars. It questions the current financial establishment as well as political prospects through the abstract story of terraforming and settling another planet and its imaginary characters and communities.'),
