(19418789, '', 'Applicant 4969', 1590449, 'Giant Wings: The Bolsover Dragonfly', 16, 1.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 1, 1, 24, 'Q4', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Organisation', 'East Midlands', 'Bolsover', 'Derbyshire', 'Bolsover', 7, 'N', 1, '6 weeks', 6, 1, 0, 'Ot', 'Visual arts', '#REF!', 'East Midlands', 'To create a giant illuminated dragonfly to exhibit at Creswell Crags and at regional events including Nottingham Light Night. The illuminated artwork will be developed in conjunction with Junction Arts and Bolsover Junior School and will be constructed in a series of workshops led by Arts Practitioners and Heritage Officers. \n'),
