(19423281, '', 'Applicant 4979', 1609021, 'Step Up', 16, 10.0, 'No', 'OFFERED', 10, 10, 31, 'Q4', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 1, 'Organisation', 'London', 'Westminster North', 'Greater London', 'Westminster', 15, 'Y', 1, '6 weeks', 7, 0, 0, 'Ot', 'Not art form specific', '#REF!', 'London', 'Step Up will empower disadvantaged young people to initiate, produce and present their own creative projects with their peers.  It will give  a creative voice to those from backgrounds underrepresented in the arts; create dynamic new works in a range of mediums; develop professional skills; and offer Arts Award qualifications.'),
