(19469689, '', 'Applicant 5052', 19469687, 'Artist in residency within Europe', 22, 1.0, 'No', 'REJECTED', 1, 0, 14, 'Q4', '2011/2012', '2011/2012', 'Lottery', 'Grants for the arts', '', 0, 'Individual', 'London', 'Twickenham', 'Greater London', 'Richmond upon Thames', 0, 'N', 0, '6 weeks', 8, 0, 0, 'Ot', 'Visual arts', '#REF!', 'London', 'The Chelsea Student Awards would like your help with the aim of rewarding young artists in their transition from art institution to the art world. This involves continuing their practice in residencies abroad, specifically Berlin, Germany and Ljubljana, Slovenia.'),
